description: Youtube Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqEhUfvHxb5DrM1WYi5VXgg More people need to be playing Perplexing Chimera. Grind Them Into Dust is a midrange control deck with a primary focus on advantage. You want to create your window by giving the players other things they need to worry about, and then seize that window after interaction is used to combo out.
